item.title: Safezone error - it wont make areas safezone
item.dc:creator: @inferno_vann inferno vann
item.description:
@inferno_vann wrote:

Okay, i had the same problem making safe zones. And here is how to fix it…

|| (absX >= SWXX && absX <= NEXX && absY >= SWYY && absY <= NEYY)

Here is what this is…

Most guides tell you to use the North West and South East coordinates. That did not work for me, so i just played with it for a while. And i figured out that… For some servers, like mine, it is South West, and North East.

So you should just put the South West X coordinates in the SWXX, and the South West Y coordinates in the SWYY. Same with the North East.

Hope that helped,
Inferno.
